Text.string: Stop in the name of the law-bot!
Where do you think you're going?
I'm here to protect my job and serve your ass.
Hands in the air! All of 'em!
All right, back to the barn!
Be on the lookout for... well, them.
I'll let you off with a warning!
Let that be a warning to ya!
Look at me! I did this to you! Remember me! [“A Bronx Tale” quote]
Now go get your shine box!
Oh, you just gonna stand there and bleed?
Woop! Woop! It's the sound of the police!
Bad boys, bad boys... whatcha gonna do?
It was fun while it lasted.
You just signed your death warrant!
Wow, you're really going for it...
Be advised, mech on the field!
You walked onto the wroooong beat!
Suspect has doubled. Repeat, suspect has doubled!
Put some holes in that thing!
Do you have a permit for that?
I'm taking you downtown for that.
We got you surrounded! Sort of!
He only had three weeks left till retirement!
What did you do that for?
Bake him away, toys! Ach, dammit.
Hey, that was my long arm of the law!
Gonna need help cuffing you now!
Plenty more in the stock room!
That's going on your permanent record!
Ooh, somebody needs an attitude adjustment!
I'll give you a free shot!
I live to cop another day!
That is SEVERAL too many murders!
Gonna take a lotta hush money for me to unsee that!
Stop now, I'll let you off with a warning!
Ever consider a career in law enforcement?
I order you to stop murdering!
